âœ… SQL Injection (unsafe queries in code)
âœ… XSS (unescaped user input in HTML)
âœ… Hardcoded passwords (found in strings)
âœ… Insecure API usage (missing auth checks in code)
âœ… Command injection (use of unsafe exec() in code)
âœ… CSRF (missing anti-CSRF tokens in forms)
âœ… Sensitive data exposure (storing passwords without hashing)
